title: #829 RHOC: The Midterm Elective Surgery Results Are In!
description:
Shannon and Vicki had dueling nips and tucks on the latest Real Housewives of Orange County, and we are here with minute by minute coverage of all the breaking news! What we know is that Shannon had to pick a dream and Vicki covered her face with a scarf afterwards. Meanwhile, Gina pissed off Tamra, and Emily went to therapy. Somehow we cracked up the entire time. Come listen to our recap!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.

author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (Ben Mandelker & Ronnie Karam)
